438
00:34:42,520 --> 00:34:44,180
 Dakle,

439
00:34:44,180 --> 00:34:47,180
 isto tako

440
00:34:47,180 --> 00:34:49,180
 nadbiskup Franić

441
00:34:49,180 --> 00:34:50,200
 i mnogi drugi,

442
00:34:50,200 --> 00:34:52,400
 dakle, tako da je on ispovjedao

443
00:34:52,400 --> 00:34:53,220
 po cijeli dan,

444
00:34:53,220 --> 00:34:53,940
 da je

445
00:34:53,940 --> 00:34:55,600
 guardijan samostana

446
00:34:55,600 --> 00:34:57,180
 morao često puta

447
00:34:57,180 --> 00:34:57,720
 intervenirati.

448
00:34:57,720 --> 00:35:00,960
 tražiti ga da prestane ispovjedati.

449
00:35:00,960 --> 00:35:03,160
 Odnosno, oni bi ponekad zatvorili,

450
00:35:03,160 --> 00:35:04,780
 ali jednostavno je bilo tako,

451
00:35:04,780 --> 00:35:06,760
 pogotovo kad je on postao,

452
00:35:06,760 --> 00:35:08,400
 mislim, bio više bolestan,

453
00:35:08,400 --> 00:35:09,660
 pa je imao prizemlju

454
00:35:09,660 --> 00:35:11,720
 kod kapele svoju sobitu

455
00:35:11,720 --> 00:35:14,560
 i onda jednostavno je bio problem,

456
00:35:14,560 --> 00:35:16,280
 on bi kasnio s ručkom,

457
00:35:16,280 --> 00:35:19,100
 ručak je uvijek u samo stanu

458
00:35:19,100 --> 00:35:19,940
 u 12 i po,

459
00:35:19,940 --> 00:35:23,300
 dakle, negdje zbog studija

460
00:35:23,300 --> 00:35:25,800
 gdje onda bude u jedan i tako,

461
00:35:25,800 --> 00:35:27,180
 ali redov to je u 12 i po

462
00:35:27,180 --> 00:35:30,120
 i on nekada ne bi jednostavno ručao.

463
00:35:30,120 --> 00:35:31,600
 Jer bi ispovjedao.

464
00:35:31,600 --> 00:35:32,240
 Jer bi ispovjedao.

465
00:35:32,240 --> 00:35:32,520
 Jer bi ispovjedao.

466
00:35:32,520 --> 00:35:35,400
 A bili su, dakle, silni,

467
00:35:35,400 --> 00:35:36,860
 dakle, redove su bili naprosto,

468
00:35:36,860 --> 00:35:37,240
 dakle,

469
00:35:37,240 --> 00:35:39,980
 i onda je imao jedno vrijeme

470
00:35:39,980 --> 00:35:41,780
 kad je primao redovnice,

471
00:35:41,780 --> 00:35:43,020
 redovnike, svećanike,

472
00:35:43,020 --> 00:35:44,500
 a onda kad je primao lajke.

473
00:35:44,500 --> 00:35:47,780
 Ali je što trenok ovog njegovog

474
00:35:47,780 --> 00:35:50,320
 odgojiteljskog rada.

475
00:35:50,320 --> 00:35:52,860
 Dakle, on je bio na glasu

476
00:35:52,860 --> 00:35:55,040
 da je s jedne strane bio izravan,

477
00:35:55,040 --> 00:35:57,020
 a s druge strane da je bio jako nježan.

478
00:35:57,020 --> 00:35:58,680
 Dakle, on je,

479
00:35:58,680 --> 00:36:01,380
 postoji, dakle,

480
00:36:01,380 --> 00:36:04,200
 postoje stereotipi

481
00:36:04,200 --> 00:36:06,360
 kad se radi ispovjedao o ispovjednicima.

482
00:36:06,360 --> 00:36:07,820
 Neki su strogi,

483
00:36:07,820 --> 00:36:10,300
 ali velika većina ispovjednika,

484
00:36:10,300 --> 00:36:12,860
 dakle, nastoje ipak biti

485
00:36:12,860 --> 00:36:14,120
 kad došli ljudi s problemima,

486
00:36:14,120 --> 00:36:16,680
 ne koriti ih, dakle,

487
00:36:17,680 --> 00:36:19,440
 pogotovo ako dođu ljudi

488
00:36:19,440 --> 00:36:20,680
 koji ne dolaze redovito.

489
00:36:20,680 --> 00:36:22,800
 Ali onda kad dolaze redovito,

490
00:36:22,800 --> 00:36:24,020
 treba naći jedan način,

491
00:36:24,020 --> 00:36:24,740
 ja isto imam

492
00:36:24,740 --> 00:36:26,760
 mišljenje i pristup

493
00:36:26,760 --> 00:36:28,820
 da treba biti blag.

494
00:36:28,820 --> 00:36:30,720
 Jer da nekada blagost

495
00:36:30,720 --> 00:36:31,420
