496
00:36:31,420 --> 00:36:32,540
 nego prekoravanje.

497
00:36:32,540 --> 00:36:34,700
 Recimo, uzet ću primjer

498
00:36:34,700 --> 00:36:36,200
 Padra Pija,

499
00:36:36,200 --> 00:36:37,040
 svetljega Pija

500
00:36:37,040 --> 00:36:38,180
 iz Pietralčine,

501
00:36:38,180 --> 00:36:39,360
 to moje rodno mjesto,

502
00:36:39,360 --> 00:36:41,280
 a slavi se u

503
00:36:41,280 --> 00:36:42,340
 Sanđavani Rotondo

504
00:36:42,340 --> 00:36:43,560
 na zapadnim obroncima

505
00:36:43,560 --> 00:36:46,480
 onoga poluotoka i brda

506
00:36:46,480 --> 00:36:47,600
 planine što ulazi

507
00:36:47,600 --> 00:36:48,480
 u Jadransko more

508
00:36:48,480 --> 00:36:50,160
 Sanđavani Rotondo,

509
00:36:50,160 --> 00:36:52,540
