510
00:36:52,540 --> 00:36:54,940
 Pogotovo kad je smatrao

511
00:36:54,940 --> 00:36:56,640
 da je netko nepotrebno dolazi,

512
00:36:56,640 --> 00:36:59,960
 izdjeću za to dva primjera,

513
00:36:59,960 --> 00:37:00,860
 koji mnogi to

514
00:37:00,860 --> 00:37:02,020
 ne znaju,

515
00:37:02,020 --> 00:37:03,360
 neki misle da otkrivaju

516
00:37:03,360 --> 00:37:04,120
 toplu vodu,

517
00:37:04,120 --> 00:37:05,260
 da se tako izrazi,

518
00:37:05,260 --> 00:37:07,100
 bio je strok prema Hrvatima

519
00:37:07,100 --> 00:37:08,720
 i zna se da je jednoj

520
00:37:08,720 --> 00:37:09,760
 gospođi iz Zagreba

521
00:37:09,760 --> 00:37:10,340
 rekao,

522
00:37:10,340 --> 00:37:12,460
 dakle, otvoreno

523
00:37:12,460 --> 00:37:13,000
 italijanski,

524
00:37:13,000 --> 00:37:14,300
 gospođa znava italijanski,

525
00:37:14,300 --> 00:37:15,480
 zašto ste došli ovdje?

526
00:37:15,480 --> 00:37:16,420
 A ona je došla

527
00:37:16,420 --> 00:37:17,800
 se njemu ispovijediti.

528
00:37:17,800 --> 00:37:18,460
 Imate oca antiča

529
00:37:18,460 --> 00:37:19,180
 u Zagrebu.

530
00:37:19,180 --> 00:37:19,800
 To je rekao

531
00:37:19,800 --> 00:37:20,940
 Kadri Pijel.

532
00:37:20,940 --> 00:37:21,340
 Da.

533
00:37:21,340 --> 00:37:22,400
 Drugi služaj,

534
00:37:22,400 --> 00:37:23,620
 jedan moj pokojni subrat

535
00:37:23,620 --> 00:37:24,540
 iz moje provincije

536
00:37:24,540 --> 00:37:25,540
 iz istoga i kraja

537
00:37:25,540 --> 00:37:26,060
 Sinjskog,

538
00:37:26,060 --> 00:37:27,640
 je došao tamo,

539
00:37:27,640 --> 00:37:29,200
 dobro, svećenicu dolazi

540
00:37:29,200 --> 00:37:30,480
 malo iz kurioznosti,

541
00:37:30,480 --> 00:37:31,140
 ajmo reći.

542
00:37:31,960 --> 00:37:34,180
 jer ima rane,

543
00:37:34,180 --> 00:37:35,260
 one su bile zavijene,

544
00:37:35,260 --> 00:37:35,780
