545
00:37:35,780 --> 00:37:38,580
 I kad je došao taj

546
00:37:38,580 --> 00:37:39,300
 k njemu,

547
00:37:39,300 --> 00:37:40,640
 a nekada su dolazili

548
00:37:40,640 --> 00:37:42,360
 malo i iz

549
00:37:42,360 --> 00:37:43,820
