550
00:37:43,820 --> 00:37:44,260
 dakle,

551
00:37:44,260 --> 00:37:45,900
 da vide je.

552
00:37:45,900 --> 00:37:47,580
 Onda je to rekao isto,

553
00:37:47,580 --> 00:37:48,680
 zašto si došao ovdje

554
00:37:48,680 --> 00:37:49,380
 tvoj subrat

555
00:37:49,380 --> 00:37:50,860
 pre Ante Antićiš

556
00:37:50,860 --> 00:37:51,740
 poveda u Zagrebu?

557
00:37:51,740 --> 00:37:53,560
 Jedan služaj je bio drugi,

558
00:37:53,560 --> 00:37:53,860
 eto,

559
00:37:53,860 --> 00:37:54,740
 dakle,

560
00:37:54,740 --> 00:37:56,320
 taj istopokojni,

