569
00:38:07,020 --> 00:38:08,480
 Mi bi to mogli pravići

570
00:38:08,480 --> 00:38:08,740
 mrzut,

571
00:38:08,740 --> 00:38:09,020
 bježi.

572
00:38:09,020 --> 00:38:10,420
 Skaparje,

573
00:38:10,420 --> 00:38:11,560
 znači pobjeći,

574
00:38:11,560 --> 00:38:12,020
 ali kad ne,

575
00:38:12,020 --> 00:38:12,940
 skapi vija,

