00:38:13,240 --> 00:38:14,120
 bježi bršića,

578
00:38:14,120 --> 00:38:14,460
 pješća.

579
00:38:14,460 --> 00:38:16,380
 Jer taj došao da vidi,

580
00:38:16,380 --> 00:38:17,860
 ja nisam naravno nikad

581
00:38:17,860 --> 00:38:18,800
 susreo padre Pija,

582
00:38:18,800 --> 00:38:19,780
 bio sam par puta

583
00:38:19,780 --> 00:38:21,720
 u San Giovanni Rotondo.

584
00:38:21,720 --> 00:38:23,120
 Dakle,

585
00:38:23,120 --> 00:38:25,240
 Frante nikad nije koristio

586
00:38:25,240 --> 00:38:26,160
 takav pristup.

587
00:38:26,160 --> 00:38:27,800
 On je bio jako,

588
00:38:27,800 --> 00:38:28,760
 jako blag.

589
00:38:29,860 --> 00:38:30,420
 dakle,

590
00:38:30,420 --> 00:38:31,960
 iznimno,

591
00:38:31,960 --> 00:38:32,780
 kad je trebalo,

592
00:38:32,780 --> 00:38:33,640
 nekom bi rekao,

593
00:38:33,640 --> 00:38:33,920
 dakle,

594
00:38:33,920 --> 00:38:34,900
 ako je netko dolazi,

595
00:38:34,900 --> 00:38:35,720
 ponavljaju se,

596
00:38:35,720 --> 00:38:36,060
 dakle,

597
00:38:36,060 --> 00:38:37,420
 problemi,

598
00:38:37,420 --> 00:38:38,480
 da ne kažem gdje si,

599
00:38:38,480 --> 00:38:39,940
 za koje se netko ispovijeda,

600
00:38:39,940 --> 00:38:42,540
 i on vidi da se taj ne trudi,

601
00:38:42,540 --> 00:38:43,300
 i tako dalje.

602
00:38:44,040 --> 00:38:46,060
 ili ako bi netko došao,

603
00:38:46,060 --> 00:38:47,780
 nekada znaju doći,

604
00:38:47,780 --> 00:38:49,880
 mi smo u samostanima isto ljudi,

605
00:38:49,880 --> 00:38:51,660
 jedovnice i redovnice,

606
00:38:51,660 --> 00:38:56,580
 pa se onda žali nekad i bespotrebno na svoga poglavara.

607
00:38:56,580 --> 00:38:58,460
 Onda bi tu prekorio.

608
00:38:58,980 --> 00:39:01,160
 ili nekada kad bi došli na ispovijed,

609
00:39:01,160 --> 00:39:01,960
 pogotovo žene,

610
00:39:01,960 --> 00:39:03,920
 pa se malo pošali na muža.

611
00:39:03,920 --> 00:39:04,980
 Sigurno,

612
00:39:04,980 --> 00:39:06,040
 nitko nije savršen.

613
00:39:06,040 --> 00:39:06,960
 Onda je,

614
00:39:06,960 --> 00:39:09,060
 jer je znalo odčitati,

615
00:39:09,060 --> 00:39:10,200
 iščitati osobu,

616
00:39:10,200 --> 00:39:12,240
 onda bi upozorio,

617
00:39:12,240 --> 00:39:12,540
 dakle,

618
00:39:12,540 --> 00:39:12,980
 na to,

619
00:39:12,980 --> 00:39:14,280
 dakle,

620
00:39:14,280 --> 00:39:17,040
 da ne dolazi samo s tim,

621
00:39:17,040 --> 00:39:18,240
 nego da se više okupi,

622
00:39:18,240 --> 00:39:21,360
 odnosno zaokupi svojim osobnim.

623
00:39:21,420 --> 00:39:23,140
 A da ne ispovijedam muževljeve grijehe.

624
00:39:23,140 --> 00:39:24,380
 To imate ljudi,

625
00:39:24,380 --> 00:39:26,020
 ja ću reći moje iskustvo jedno,

626
00:39:26,020 --> 00:39:26,660
 koje je sigurno zanimljivo.

627
00:39:26,660 --> 00:39:28,360
 Volimo tuđe grijehe ispovijedati.

628
00:39:28,360 --> 00:39:30,160
 Ja sam kao mlad bio u gospe,

629
00:39:30,160 --> 00:39:32,160
 dobio sam godom dana u Imotskoj krajini,

630
00:39:32,160 --> 00:39:33,960
 dakle,

631
00:39:33,960 --> 00:39:37,160
 a onda sam premijestveno uspito odmah u gospe od zdravlja,

632
00:39:37,160 --> 00:39:40,520
 i tamo sam uz dvadesetak sati vjeronauka,

633
00:39:40,520 --> 00:39:42,960
 i bio mi određen jedan studij,

634
00:39:42,960 --> 00:39:43,960
 to je žurnalistika,

635
00:39:43,960 --> 00:39:45,720
 na koji nisam prispio ni ni važno,

636
00:39:45,720 --> 00:39:48,960
 jer kad sam zvršio fakultet,

637
00:39:49,040 --> 00:39:50,440
 mogao sam i bez toga pisati,

638
00:39:50,440 --> 00:39:52,660
 onda sam posjeto ga prispio u Urij,

639
00:39:52,660 --> 00:39:56,220
 dakle, nakon tri godine pastoralne službe,

640
00:39:56,220 --> 00:39:57,580
 i to mi je dragocijeno vrijeme,

641
00:39:57,580 --> 00:39:58,940
 ispovijedao sam,

642
00:39:58,940 --> 00:40:01,680
 jer smo imali raspored,

643
00:40:01,680 --> 00:40:03,600
 i dođe jedna gozbođa, starija,

644
00:40:03,600 --> 00:40:05,340
 i ona se ispovijedi,

645
00:40:05,340 --> 00:40:07,780
 to mogu reći jer nije otkrivanje ispovijedne tajne,

646
00:40:07,780 --> 00:40:10,900
 i ispovijedi kratko neke svoje slabosti,

647
00:40:10,900 --> 00:40:12,240
 a ispovijedi,

648
00:40:12,240 --> 00:40:15,200
 onda podome ispovijedava deset minuta grijehe svoje nevijesti.

649
00:40:15,200 --> 00:40:18,120
 I ja, onako funcorski na kraju,

650
00:40:19,040 --> 00:40:20,680
 prije nego ću i dati od rješenja karine.

651
00:40:20,680 --> 00:40:22,640
 To je snaha, nevijesti njena snaha.

652
00:40:22,640 --> 00:40:23,480
 Da, snaha, da, da.

653
00:40:23,480 --> 00:40:25,180
 A ova se svekrva zove.

654
00:40:25,180 --> 00:40:27,960
 Dakle, svekrva je malo svojih grijehe i puno snahini.

655
00:40:27,960 --> 00:40:30,540
 Evo, ja namjerno njoj kažem,

656
00:40:30,540 --> 00:40:32,920
 dobro, vi ste lijepo ispovijedli svoje grijehe,

657
00:40:32,920 --> 00:40:34,120
 niste ih imali puno,

658
00:40:34,120 --> 00:40:37,640
 eto, izmolit ćete tri zdravo Marije za svoje grijehe.

659
00:40:37,640 --> 00:40:39,420
 A ispovijedli ste grijehe svoje snahe,

660
00:40:39,420 --> 00:40:40,540
 ona je velika grešnica.

661
00:40:40,540 --> 00:40:43,680
 Lijepo vi ispovijedite,

662
00:40:43,680 --> 00:40:46,400
 odnosno, izmolite pokoru za njene grijehe,

663
00:40:46,400 --> 00:40:49,460
 jedno, jedno, ovaj, dio rožarija.

664
00:40:49,460 --> 00:40:50,600
 Krunice, to znači,

665
00:40:50,600 --> 00:40:53,220
 na primjer, radosna ili,

666
00:40:53,220 --> 00:40:55,380
 i u to vrijeme su bila slavna i žalostna,

667
00:40:55,380 --> 00:40:56,940
 peto tajstava.

668
00:40:56,940 --> 00:40:59,140
 Ona nije čekala od rješenja utekla,

669
00:40:59,140 --> 00:41:00,980
 je van i tražila gvardijana da nje prijavi.

670
00:41:00,980 --> 00:41:04,000
 A gvardijan je bio igrom slučaja u vratariji.

671
00:41:04,000 --> 00:41:06,320
 I onda traži gvardijana, kaže, on, ja sam.

672
00:41:06,320 --> 00:41:08,660
 On je intuirao da se ona nešto njutila

673
00:41:08,660 --> 00:41:10,540
 i kaže, on, onaj vaš mladi,

674
00:41:10,540 --> 00:41:12,000
 tamo što je ispovijedla, je bezbožan.

675
00:41:12,000 --> 00:41:13,300
 To je ona za vas rekla.

676
00:41:13,300 --> 00:41:16,000
 Da. Kaže, zato što mi je dao pokoru

677
00:41:16,000 --> 00:41:17,700
 peto tajstava.

678
00:41:17,700 --> 00:41:18,780
 A zašto mi je dao?

679
00:41:18,780 --> 00:41:21,060
 Pa ja sam rekla, grijehe moje nevijeste.

680
00:41:21,060 --> 00:41:23,320
 Jes, bezbožan je malovan,

681
00:41:23,360 --> 00:41:24,940
 dao, trebam dao 15-15.

682
00:41:24,940 --> 00:41:27,760
 Ali, da, dakle,

683
00:41:27,760 --> 00:41:30,220
 to je u stvari su bile situacije

684
00:41:30,220 --> 00:41:32,060
 u kojima bi Frant Antić bio malo...

685
00:41:32,060 --> 00:41:32,540
 Stroži.

686
00:41:32,540 --> 00:41:33,220
 Stroži, da.

687
00:41:33,220 --> 00:41:34,660
 A on je, inače, meni je,

688
00:41:34,660 --> 00:41:38,480
 on je, Frant Antić je u rodu sa mojim ocem,

689
00:41:38,480 --> 00:41:40,920
 dakle, to isto je zato na kod Šibenika.

690
00:41:40,920 --> 00:41:43,400
 I moj mi je tata ispričao kako je on

691
00:41:43,400 --> 00:41:46,980
 njemu, dakle, kako su oni,

692
00:41:46,980 --> 00:41:48,080
 mislim, jedan njegov brat,

693
00:41:48,080 --> 00:41:50,840
 kako im je rekao što će biti,

694
00:41:50,840 --> 00:41:53,180
 što je ono na čemu će oni trebati,

695
00:41:53,340 --> 00:41:55,280
 s čim će se oni trebati boriti u svojoj naravi.

696
00:41:55,280 --> 00:41:57,900
 I da on to do dan danas,

697
00:41:57,900 --> 00:41:59,260
 kroz cijeli svoj život,

698
00:41:59,260 --> 00:42:01,060
 je to istina bila,

699
00:42:01,060 --> 00:42:02,520
 dakle, u njegovoj naravi,

700
00:42:02,520 --> 00:42:03,840
 to je bilo ono što je on trebao,

701
00:42:03,840 --> 00:42:06,000
 s čime se on trebao pozabaviti.

702
00:42:06,000 --> 00:42:08,200
 Ali, baš mi isto to uvijek prenosio

703
00:42:08,200 --> 00:42:09,000
 i preko mog djeda,

704
00:42:09,000 --> 00:42:11,600
 tu njegovu ljubav i nježnost prema ljudima.

705
00:42:11,680 --> 00:42:14,180
 A kakav je on bio kao subrat u zajednici,

706
00:42:14,180 --> 00:42:15,360
 dakle, vašoj,

707
00:42:15,360 --> 00:42:17,420
 u majci Bođe Lurdskoj?

708
00:42:17,420 --> 00:42:20,220
 On je bio vrlo skroman i jednostavan.

709
00:42:20,220 --> 00:42:24,140
 Tu u Zagrebu je bio još jedan fratra

710
00:42:24,140 --> 00:42:26,140
 koji je iz daleka njemu sličio.

711
00:42:26,700 --> 00:42:27,720
 Taj nije bio svećenik,

712
00:42:27,720 --> 00:42:28,300
 bio je brat.

713
00:42:28,300 --> 00:42:30,220
 Isto to za učastni brat,

714
00:42:30,220 --> 00:42:31,400
 ko od nas kažu brat lajk,

715
00:42:31,400 --> 00:42:32,940
 to je malo ružna riječ u latinskom,

716
00:42:32,940 --> 00:42:35,180
 neznalica, lajk je izlazi iz puka.

717
00:42:35,180 --> 00:42:37,880
 E, i grom slučaja,

718
00:42:37,880 --> 00:42:39,880
 jednom su došli, došli su, dakle,

719
00:42:39,880 --> 00:42:42,800
 ili gimnazijalci, klerici,

720
00:42:42,800 --> 00:42:46,360
 jer su već se oblačili za drugog gimnazije,

721
00:42:46,360 --> 00:42:48,400
 ili su bili već bogoslovi

722
00:42:48,400 --> 00:42:49,220
 i vidjeli su njega,

723
00:42:49,220 --> 00:42:50,740
 vidjeli su toga brata,

724
00:42:50,740 --> 00:42:52,840
 koji nije bio fratar,

725
00:42:52,840 --> 00:42:54,760
 i mislili su da je,

726
00:42:55,160 --> 00:42:56,340
 onda su vidjeli su Frantu

727
00:42:56,340 --> 00:42:57,460
 i mislili su da je taj brat.

728
00:42:57,460 --> 00:43:00,520
 I onda su počeli oko njega,

729
00:43:00,520 --> 00:43:02,460
 mislim da se zvao Lovro,

730
00:43:02,460 --> 00:43:03,480
 Fra Lovro, ovo, ono,

731
00:43:03,480 --> 00:43:04,900
 Franti se ništa ni ne ljuti,

732
00:43:04,900 --> 00:43:05,680
 nego odgovarao,

733
00:43:05,680 --> 00:43:06,400
 glumirao je.

734
00:43:06,400 --> 00:43:10,780
 Drugi je, drugi primjer je,

735
00:43:10,780 --> 00:43:13,460
 koliko je on na momente bio jednostavan,

736
00:43:13,460 --> 00:43:15,920
 on je bio posvećen duhovnom životu

737
00:43:15,920 --> 00:43:19,680
 i mnoge stvari iz praktičnog života nije znao,

738
00:43:19,680 --> 00:43:23,320
 ali je neke stvari bio prunicljiv.

739
00:43:23,920 --> 00:43:24,960
 i mi smo imali tada,

740
00:43:24,960 --> 00:43:27,000
 sad je to u parkiralište zbog gradova,

741
00:43:27,000 --> 00:43:30,140
 imali smo vrt gdje je se sadilo povrće

742
00:43:30,140 --> 00:43:30,800
 i jasno,

743
00:43:30,800 --> 00:43:34,500
 imaju samostan iz tog vrta povrće.

744
00:43:35,360 --> 00:43:41,400
 i trebalo je prekopati cijeli vrt za posadi proljetnu turu povrća

745
00:43:41,400 --> 00:43:44,660
 i bogoslov su to sve lijepo prekopali dosta brzo

746
00:43:44,660 --> 00:43:51,940
 i onda je on njih pitao što bi oni željeli.

747
00:43:51,940 --> 00:43:56,300
 A on je bio kao magister taj koji je dozvolio da bogoslov igraju nogomet,

748
00:43:56,580 --> 00:43:57,940
 i to bez habita.

749
00:43:57,940 --> 00:43:59,300
 A, on im je reko mogu dozvolio?

750
00:43:59,300 --> 00:44:00,060
 On je dozvolio to.

751
00:44:00,060 --> 00:44:02,800
 Jer imao, on imao pravo to dozvolio.

752
00:44:02,800 --> 00:44:08,380
 I oni su rekli njemu da bi im trebalo kupiti nekakve kopačke.

753
00:44:08,380 --> 00:44:13,780
 To su cipele, nisu tenice, to su cipele zegre na trali za baš nogomet.

754
00:44:13,780 --> 00:44:16,640
 I on je došao gvardijanu i kaže,

755
00:44:16,640 --> 00:44:18,000
 evo, brzo su prekopali vrt,

756
00:44:18,000 --> 00:44:20,080
 gvardijan je bio zadovoljan, čak ih je počastio,

757
00:44:20,080 --> 00:44:21,600
 prošto to mi li sirom, ne znam nija.

758
00:44:21,600 --> 00:44:23,380
 I kaže fra Ante,

759
00:44:23,380 --> 00:44:26,260
 gvardijanu, evo, on imao jednu želju, koju?

760
00:44:26,260 --> 00:44:28,480
 Kaže da im se kupe kopačke.

761
00:44:28,480 --> 00:44:32,780
 Ante mislio da su to one lopate uske kojima se grči.

762
00:44:32,800 --> 00:44:34,880
 I onda se gvardijan najljutio.

763
00:44:34,880 --> 00:44:39,860
 On je dostavno ne pristupio.

764
00:44:39,860 --> 00:44:41,760
 Mislio da oni žele kopati.

765
00:44:41,760 --> 00:44:42,500
 Još bolje kopati.

766
00:44:42,500 --> 00:44:43,980
 Još bolje pa da im to kupe.

767
00:44:43,980 --> 00:44:44,820
 Pa se najljutio.

768
00:44:44,820 --> 00:44:49,020
 To pokazuje da on neke stvari iz praktičnog života nije znao.

769
00:44:49,020 --> 00:44:52,940
 Ali on je prorekao da će ići bogoslovo u civilo

770
00:44:52,940 --> 00:44:54,180
 kad krenu na fakultet

771
00:44:54,180 --> 00:44:56,360
 i dozvolio je da igraju novomet.

772
00:44:56,360 --> 00:44:58,940
 Što recimo u Makarsku nije bilo dozvoljeno.

773
00:44:58,940 --> 00:45:00,720
 Mogli su igrati, ali u dugoj robi.

774
00:45:01,140 --> 00:45:03,080
 A bi on je dozvolio da joj igraju

775
00:45:03,080 --> 00:45:06,000
 kao i drugi kad se bave športa.

776
00:45:06,000 --> 00:45:07,680
 S druge strane,

777
00:45:07,680 --> 00:45:09,320
 valja reći i to da je on

778
00:45:09,320 --> 00:45:11,560
 znao reći savjetovati.

779
00:45:11,560 --> 00:45:13,400
 Naprimjer, kad bi

780
00:45:13,400 --> 00:45:15,240
 nego kod njemu dolazio,

781
00:45:15,240 --> 00:45:17,260
 naprimjer,

782
00:45:17,260 --> 00:45:19,280
 koji je bio u sjemeništu,

783
00:45:19,280 --> 00:45:21,060
 pogotovo u gimnaziji,

784
00:45:21,060 --> 00:45:22,200
 ili dolazio iz

785
00:45:22,200 --> 00:45:24,900
 kandidature djevojke

786
00:45:24,900 --> 00:45:26,840
 koje su bile kandarkinje

787
00:45:26,840 --> 00:45:28,560
 za časne sestre,

788
00:45:28,560 --> 00:45:31,240
 on bi znao reći

789
00:45:31,240 --> 00:45:32,400
 onima koji nisu za to,

790
00:45:32,400 --> 00:45:33,980
 ima slučajeva,

791
00:45:33,980 --> 00:45:35,580
 to su neki čak svjedočili,

792
00:45:35,580 --> 00:45:37,620
 dragi sinko,

793
00:45:37,620 --> 00:45:38,300
 dragak čeri,

794
00:45:38,300 --> 00:45:39,620
 idi u svijet,

795
00:45:39,620 --> 00:45:40,900
 osnovi obitelj,

796
00:45:40,900 --> 00:45:42,240
 zate nije ovo zvanje.

797
00:45:42,240 --> 00:45:44,040
 I to na jedan vrlo lijep način.

798
00:45:44,080 --> 00:45:44,420
 Pa da.

799
00:45:44,420 --> 00:45:46,220
 Onda, ako su neki dolazili,

800
00:45:46,220 --> 00:45:48,240
 pa su uvijek bili

801
00:45:48,240 --> 00:45:49,180
 s nekim problemima,

802
00:45:49,180 --> 00:45:49,780
 jer su bili,

803
00:45:49,780 --> 00:45:50,780
 znači,

804
00:45:50,780 --> 00:45:51,720
 opterećeni,

805
00:45:51,720 --> 00:45:53,860
 ili su imali probleme

806
00:45:53,860 --> 00:45:54,760
 sa odgojiteljima,

807
00:45:54,760 --> 00:45:55,300
 pa se žali,

808
00:45:55,300 --> 00:45:56,280
 oni uvijek nastaju

809
00:45:56,280 --> 00:45:57,280
 na jedan lijep način.

810
00:45:57,280 --> 00:45:57,980
 Dakle,

811
00:45:57,980 --> 00:46:00,680
 nije korio u smislu strogom,

812
00:46:00,680 --> 00:46:02,580
 jer ja isto osobno smatram,

813
00:46:02,580 --> 00:46:04,600
 pogotovo kad netko dođe na,

814
00:46:04,600 --> 00:46:06,220
 dakle, pogotovo nisam

815
00:46:06,220 --> 00:46:07,820
 duhovni vođao dotičnoj osobi

816
00:46:07,820 --> 00:46:09,320
 i pogotovo kad je gužva

817
00:46:09,320 --> 00:46:10,100
 u ispovjedanju,

818
00:46:10,100 --> 00:46:11,940
 dati osnovne savjete

819
00:46:11,940 --> 00:46:13,020
 i dati odriješenje,

820
00:46:13,740 --> 00:46:15,300
 a ne prekoravati.

821
00:46:15,300 --> 00:46:17,020
 Bez obžira u kojim se

822
00:46:17,020 --> 00:46:18,020
 gresima radilo.

823
00:46:18,020 --> 00:46:21,020
 Dakle, jer...

824
00:46:21,020 --> 00:46:23,140
 Ali ono što ste rekli u stvari

825
00:46:23,140 --> 00:46:25,440
 je da on je tražio,

826
00:46:25,440 --> 00:46:27,180
 on je u tom savjetovanju,

827
00:46:27,180 --> 00:46:29,320
 u ispovjedi ili u duhovnom vodstvu

828
00:46:29,320 --> 00:46:32,100
 je jednima davao smjernice

829
00:46:32,100 --> 00:46:33,520
 da nije zvanje za njih,

830
00:46:33,520 --> 00:46:35,640
 druge je snažijuc u njihovom zvanju,

831
00:46:35,640 --> 00:46:37,420
 dakle, tražiči Božju volju

832
00:46:37,420 --> 00:46:38,700
 u njihovim životima u stvari,

833
00:46:38,700 --> 00:46:40,220
 pomažući njima da ju otkriju.

834
00:46:40,220 --> 00:46:42,360
 Dakle, on je uvijek nastupravo to,

835
00:46:42,360 --> 00:46:43,220
 dakle, da osoba,

836
00:46:43,400 --> 00:46:46,560
 spozna što Bog pred nju stavlja.

837
00:46:46,560 --> 00:46:48,940
 On se nije, naprijed,

838
00:46:48,940 --> 00:46:50,440
 nekad ali i bio savjetovati,

839
00:46:50,440 --> 00:46:52,520
 gdje su nedavno u tekstu,

840
00:46:52,520 --> 00:46:53,820
 neki, da li ne znam,

841
00:46:53,820 --> 00:46:56,000
 da li su tiskovine ili portali

842
00:46:56,000 --> 00:46:58,380
 ovi elektronički,

843
00:46:59,140 --> 00:47:02,680
 donio su da je on savjetovao Kuhariću

844
00:47:02,680 --> 00:47:09,440
 da uči jezike i da ako može upiše doktora dok je bio župnik u Samoboru,

845
00:47:09,440 --> 00:47:12,760
 jer ga čeka budućnost dosta zahtjevna.

846
00:47:13,800 --> 00:47:16,400
 on je nešto učio.

847
00:47:16,400 --> 00:47:17,180
 I to je Fran Tantić savjetovao.

848
00:47:17,180 --> 00:47:17,760
 Da, da, savjeto.

849
00:47:17,760 --> 00:47:19,340
 I konkretan savjet mu je rekao.

850
00:47:19,340 --> 00:47:20,960
 To je sluga Božji, dakle,

851
00:47:20,960 --> 00:47:23,580
 sam to je izjavio,

852
00:47:23,580 --> 00:47:24,560
 dakle, nije to da nešto mi je sam...

853
00:47:24,560 --> 00:47:28,280
 Ha, to je on rekao da je on savjetovo to kardinalo Kuhariću.

854
00:47:28,280 --> 00:47:31,120
 Da, da, ne Ante, nego to je izjavio baš Kuharić sam.

855
00:47:31,120 --> 00:47:31,500
 Da, da.

856
00:47:31,500 --> 00:47:35,160
 Dakle, on nije studirao za doktorat,

857
00:47:35,160 --> 00:47:36,760
 ali je dobio počasnih doktora,

858
00:47:36,760 --> 00:47:40,300
 ali je nešto naučio jezik jer je bio najprije pomoćniji biskup,

859
00:47:40,300 --> 00:47:43,160
 onda nadbiskup i kardinal metropolita Zagrebački.

860
00:47:43,160 --> 00:47:46,600
 Dakle, on je to sam posvjedočio.

861
00:47:46,600 --> 00:47:49,740
 Anteć je znao takve savjete savjetovati

862
00:47:49,740 --> 00:47:51,620
 ili je znao o svećanicima,

863
00:47:51,620 --> 00:47:53,840
 nekima kod kojih je to vidio,

864
00:47:53,840 --> 00:47:56,480
 koji su ponekad zbog svoje,

865
00:47:56,600 --> 00:47:58,980
 bili su kolerici, ja to svačavam,

866
00:47:58,980 --> 00:48:00,740
 jer i ja sam dijelom kolerik sam,

867
00:48:00,740 --> 00:48:02,680
 guinik sam, ali više kolerik,

868
00:48:02,680 --> 00:48:04,740
 dakle, koji su imali određene darove,

869
00:48:04,740 --> 00:48:09,600
 pa su onda zbog ti darova nekada bili malo tapkani po glavi,

870
00:48:09,600 --> 00:48:10,800
 kako to odgovoriti i radi.

871
00:48:10,800 --> 00:48:13,420
 On je rekao, brate moj, bude strpljiv,

872
00:48:13,420 --> 00:48:16,680
 radi na svojoj duhovnoj,

873
00:48:16,680 --> 00:48:19,740
 ne samo izobrazbi, nego kulture i napredko,

874
00:48:19,740 --> 00:48:24,980
 ali i na ovoj, dakle, kulturnoj, filozofkoj i tako dalje,

875
00:48:25,080 --> 00:48:26,500
 jer će ti to učigotno trebati.

876
00:48:26,500 --> 00:48:28,900
 Nekima je znao reći,

877
00:48:28,900 --> 00:48:30,760
 jer ćeš biti vrstan propovjednik,

878
00:48:30,760 --> 00:48:33,420
 jer će te zajednica poslati na studij.

879
00:48:33,420 --> 00:48:35,160
 Dakle, konkretno, da, da.

880
00:48:35,160 --> 00:48:36,960
 Dakle, onda je poticao,

881
00:48:36,960 --> 00:48:38,900
 recimo u to vrijeme, pogotovo i za rata,

882
00:48:38,900 --> 00:48:42,720
 veliki broj redovničkih zajednica,

883
00:48:42,720 --> 00:48:43,760
 častnih sestara,

884
00:48:43,760 --> 00:48:45,980
 izgubile su svoju zadaću,

885
00:48:45,980 --> 00:48:48,180
 koju su imali po karizmi svoje utemeljiteljice,

886
00:48:48,260 --> 00:48:49,380
 recimo školske sestre,

887
00:48:49,380 --> 00:48:50,940
 imale su škole,

888
00:48:50,940 --> 00:48:54,000
 križarice su radile po bolnicama,

889
00:48:54,000 --> 00:48:55,260
