890
00:48:55,260 --> 00:48:58,080
 onda je njih znao savjetovati,

891
00:48:58,080 --> 00:49:01,880
 dakle, da se okrenu,

892
00:49:01,880 --> 00:49:04,300
 da nauče nešto svirati,

893
00:49:04,300 --> 00:49:04,960
 i okrene se,

894
00:49:04,960 --> 00:49:06,440
 odkrenu se nekako,

895
00:49:06,440 --> 00:49:07,380
