896
00:49:07,380 --> 00:49:08,980
 teološko ili drugo izobrazbi,

897
00:49:08,980 --> 00:49:11,500
 jer će biti pozvane na žup.

898
00:49:11,540 --> 00:49:13,800
 Pogotovo recimo,

899
00:49:13,800 --> 00:49:15,720
 ja sam imao u svojoj obitelji,

900
00:49:15,720 --> 00:49:17,700
 imam i sada dosta živih,

901
00:49:17,700 --> 00:49:19,280
