904
00:49:21,780 --> 00:49:23,160
 Blago vama.

905
00:49:23,160 --> 00:49:24,180
 Očevu sestru,

906
00:49:24,180 --> 00:49:25,200
 maminu sestru,

907
00:49:25,200 --> 00:49:27,980
 od tatine tetke kćer,

908
00:49:27,980 --> 00:49:30,640
 od mamina brata u dujaka kćer,

909
00:49:30,640 --> 00:49:33,140
 od mamine dvije tetke po kćeri,

910
00:49:33,140 --> 00:49:34,240
 od jedne dvije unuke,

911
00:49:34,240 --> 00:49:36,880
 dakle, onda sam imao...

912
00:49:36,880 --> 00:49:38,080
 Puna kućare dobroća.

913
00:49:38,080 --> 00:49:40,600
 Dakle, onda baš jedna je bila medicinska sestra,

914
00:49:40,720 --> 00:49:42,260
